This assignment was given in order to explore the idea of not storing passwords in certain ways. The write up gives a clearer picture of how password compromising took place. Please read there.

NOTE: When I say hash cracking, we're not actually cracking hashes as they are one way functions. We are hashing the passwords and comparing against the known hashes in the hash list that were stored in the company's database.

Use of this code in any form for academic purposes is considered cheating, which is not only unfair to your classmates,
but as well as yourself. Use at your own risk.
